data.description: When you drive up you'll see an all brick home that has been meticulously cared for. The attention to detail in this home is quite refreshing and it has the upgrades most people are searching for such as granite counters, stainless steel appliances, including a double oven, new cooktop and new exhaust hood. In other words this home is ready to live in. The  master bedroom is spacious and the masterbath has a soaker tub to relax in for those sore muscles. This home is located out in the rural area of Hilliard where you can have horses, chickens and various other farm animals. The property is located 1.6 miles from the Public Boat ramp on the beautiful St Marys River. The other bedrooms in this home are plenty large enough and the trayed ceilings are very desirable. You have to come see this spacious open floor plan home to appreciate it. You also have a detached garage with electric and 2 roll-up doors and approximately 20' ceilings so talk about a man cave, this is it! See this soon!!!
